    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_31_3",
    "text": "3).形容词(adj)：表示人或事物的性质或特征。如：good，right，white. 4)1a (num):不日争物的序。：one，two，jist，second，fourth. 5).动词(v.)：表示动作或状态。t如：am，i，are，have，see.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0856610800744879,
      0.3096179183135705,
      0.925512104283054,
      0.40118577075098816
    ],
    "page": "notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_31",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_31_4",
    "text": "b).副词(adv)：修饰动词、形容词或其他副词，说明时间，地点.程度等。 t如:now, very.here, ofben, guetly,slowly.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
