    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_31_5",
    "text": "7).冠词(art)：用在名词前，帮助说明名词。如：a，an，the.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0856610800744879,
      0.46772068511198944,
      0.7532588454376163,
      0.4927536231884058
    ],
    "page": "notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_31",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_31_6",
    "text": "8).介词(pr.)：表示它后面的名词或代词与其他句子成分的关系。如：in on, fiom, above, behind.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09124767225325885,
      0.49670619235836627,
      0.8938547486033519,
