    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_31_7",
    "text": "9).选词(cony)：用来连接词、短语或句子。如：and，but，before. 10).感叹词(interj)：表示喜、怒、哀、乐等感情。如：oh， weu，hi. 2.句子成分：英语句子成分分为七种",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
