  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_31_10",
    "text": "2).谓语动词说明主语的动作或状态，回答”做(什么)”主要由动词相任。 如: Jacdk cleans the room every day.(杰克每天打扫房间)",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
